modName: UNP TANLINES with Adorable Face and FMS body textures
summary:
Me doodling on others peoples stuff again.
I'm just a dog and it was there.
descriptionHtml:
In my opinion, the Demoniac texture package contains some of the best sets of female textures to date.
It's taken these great artists many hours to get their craft to this level of realism.
A little pink here a little bronze there. Photo analysis and all.. A lot of work to say the least.
Having said that, I wanted to see tan and tanlines (it's bikini season if you haven't noticed) and found a white bikini template. Sweet! a little layering and playing with face contrast, layering in a black transparent layer and viola! These are patchworks from several textures and blended to match and are seamless. I included the rest of the 12 file package I'm currently using with them, all made from the works of the credited artists.
It turned out okay but it gave me an idea for a tanning salon mod.. lol
